snippet.title: Fear Effect Sedna teaser
snippet.description:
FEAR EFFECT CAMPAIGN IS LIVE! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sushee/fear-effect-sedna

Do you remember that feeling? Fear Effect is back.
Hana, Rain, Glas, Deke and Axel, a newcomer, are coming for you. Let them live again. Let them kill again.

A game by Sushee with permission from Square Enix Collective.
